I’m going to make one. Pay script though. If you buy it my PowerChopper comes free along with it.
[/quote]

Ill be releasing my Draynor Chop-All script which will be a pay script soon… Currently it chops and banks Reg Trees, Oaks, Willows and Yews over night Im in the process of adding SetUp Forms, Global Statics and a Auth System before release thou… but the chopper is about 95% finished and bug free atm here’s a quick report only problem is my yew chopper guy keeps gettin box’d or some other logout random… But my chopper uses FindDeformed Bitmaps for 100% Accurate Tree Finding without Mouse Spiral, Many Lost Checkouts and is overall fairly solid.
